permissions on group:
 * visibility
   * members only
   * all users
   * public

permissions on user:
 * visibility
   * friends (& peers in groups)
   * all users
   * public

 * request contact
   * nobody
   * peers only
   * all users

policies (users)
 * burdon (share page)
   * nobody ?
   * friends only
   * friends and peers
   * all users
 * pester (notify)
   * nobody
   * friends only
   * friends and peers
   * all users
 * message
   * nobody
   * friends only
   * all users

policies (group)
 * share_policy 
   * members only
   * all users

